{
  "stem": "13315.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he said to me, look, to me that $150 doesn't mean a darn thing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You want to keep it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I owed it to you-- you were generous to loan it to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I repay my loan and give you my thanks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Martha felt the same way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was pleased.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all I met her through a friend of hers-- girlfriend-- who was married to another refugee-- one from Poland.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I saw her-- I wouldn't say it was love at first sight, but there was something about her that attracted me-- not only the exterior, but the personality.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We started going together-- going together, because I didn't want to bind her until I had at least a job at a-- I mean, for any length of time.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my first job, then we decided to get married.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Her parents were wonderful to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were not like in-laws, they were like parents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I couldn't have found better ones.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Only, unhappily, her father died about three years after we got married.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Her mother lived much longer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was a very wonderful person.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Chicago.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Father, yeah, and his wife-- they came to New York.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's when I took the bus to New York to make sure-- around to the last moment, I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They got on.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They told me that she had two brothers in Washington.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they wanted to go to Washington.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she said to me, now, you move everything and come to Washington.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, sorry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm engaged in Chicago.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That comes first.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] She didn't like that idea at all, but [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was better that way.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
